- On the countertop, there are two cups of coffee and some snacks.

- Above the dining table, there is a large light fixture hanging from the ceiling.
- To the left of the dining table, on the floor, there's a carton of eggs and a pack of groceries.
- On the right side of the image, near the fridge, there's an oven.
- In the far corner of the kitchen, a microwave is visible.
- The refrigerator has a glass shelf on top, holding various items.
- Next to the dining table, there is a bottle placed on the floor.
- A door with a window leads into another room from this kitchen area.
